    "JSON template for the tool's `arguments`. Three placeholders get substituted before sending: `{{system}}` (Daisy's system prompt), `{{transcript}}` (meeting title + body), `{{title}}` (meeting title alone). Edit the `model` field to match a model your wrapper has pulled." : {
