    "Transcripts are sent to Anthropic over HTTPS using your own API key. Create one at console.anthropic.com/settings/keys — it's stored in your macOS Keychain. Each summary costs roughly $0.01–0.05." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ru" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Транскрипты отправляются в Anthropic по HTTPS с использованием вашего собственного API-ключа. Создайте его на console.anthropic.com/settings/keys — он хранится в Keychain macOS. Каждое саммари стоит примерно $0.01–0.05."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Transcripts are sent to OpenAI over HTTPS using your own API key. Create one at platform.openai.com/api-keys — it's stored in your macOS Keychain. Each summary costs roughly $0.01–0.05." : {
